**Name and Position:**
- Name: Claire Wilkins
- Position: [Position Title will be confirmed and updated accordingly]

- Engineering

**Manager:**
- Alexander Roberts

- [To be confirmed and included once available]

**Day 1:**

- **Afternoon:** Meet the team and set up your workspace.

**Day 2:**
- **Morning:** Learn about department goals and current projects.
- **Afternoon:** Training session on internal tools and software.

**Day 3:**
- **Morning:** One-on-one meeting with your manager, Alexander Roberts.
- **Afternoon:** Shadow a team member to gain insight into ongoing projects.

**Day 4:**
- **Morning:** Participate in a workshop on company culture and values.
- **Afternoon:** Engage in a Q&A session with HR to address any onboarding questions.

**Day 5:**
- **Morning:** Provide feedback on the onboarding process.
- **Afternoon:** Review the week's learnings and set goals for the coming weeks.

**Additional Notes:**
- Ensure all necessary access credentials and equipment are provided to Claire by the end of Day 1.
- A follow-up meeting with Alexander Roberts is scheduled at the end of the first week to discuss progress and address any concerns.
